---
import BlogLayout from '../../layouts/BlogLayout.astro';
const faqs = [
  { q: 'What does "Remove Whole Numbers" mode do?', a: 'This mode removes entire number sequences (including decimals like 3.14) — leaving no trace of where the number was, other than the surrounding space.' },
  { q: 'What does "Remove Digits Only" mode do?', a: 'This mode removes individual digit characters but leaves the rest of the word. For example, "h3llo" becomes "hllo".' },
  { q: 'Will it remove numbers inside words?', a: 'In Remove Digits mode, yes. In Remove Whole Numbers mode, only standalone number sequences are removed.' },
  { q: 'Can I remove numbers from multiple lines at once?', a: 'Yes — paste as many lines as you need and the tool processes all of them simultaneously.' },
];
---
<BlogLayout
  title="How to Remove Numbers from Text Online Free"
  description="Remove all numbers or just digits from text instantly. Choose Remove Digits mode or Remove Whole Numbers mode. Free online number remover."
  canonical="/blog/how-to-remove-numbers-from-text-online"
  date="2026-07-02"
  readTime="3 min read"
  category="Text Utilities"
  faqs={faqs}
>
  <p>Need to strip numbers from a block of text for analysis, formatting, or cleaning? This tool removes numbers instantly with two modes: remove individual digit characters or remove entire numeric sequences.</p>

  <h2>How to Remove Numbers from Text</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>Paste your text into the input box.</li>
    <li>Choose <strong>Remove Digits</strong> (removes each digit character) or <strong>Remove Whole Numbers</strong> (removes entire number sequences).</li>
    <li>Copy the clean output.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2>Use Cases</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Cleaning data for text analysis</li>
    <li>Removing page numbers from pasted PDFs</li>
    <li>Stripping reference numbers from legal documents</li>
    <li>Preprocessing text for NLP models</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="my-8 p-5 bg-violet-950/40 border border-violet-800/50 rounded-2xl text-center">
    <p class="text-slate-300 mb-3">Remove numbers from text in one click — free</p>
    <a href="/tools/remove-numbers" class="inline-block bg-violet-600 hover:bg-violet-500 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl transition-colors">Open Remove Numbers Tool →</a>
  </div>
</BlogLayout>
